{"tid":370043,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[無圖]屌你老味床頭有隻蜜蜂咁大隻嘅蟻","createTime":"2017-08-22T19:03:19.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-23T05:20:09.000Z","uid":135707,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"576de61d6bc8174a01cb693a618fd7f2ec993c54","tid":370043,"uid":135707,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-22T19:03:19.000Z","msg":"可能你會鬧我廢 但我由細到大至撚驚螞蟻 蜜蜂都係 無論大隻定細隻都好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 覺得螞蟻同蜜蜂個身嗰幾節郁郁下勁核突<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 諗起都打冷陣<br />\n<br />\n頭先碌碌下連登 眼尾望到床頭有粒黑粒郁嚟郁去 我嗰陣已經驚驚地 再望真啲係一隻有手指尾頭個節咁大隻嘅螞蟻 當堂嚇撚到無左反應 大隻到我可以好清楚咁睇到佢啲手腳同個嘴個夾仲有對眼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 但係點都要捉左佢先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 跟住雞手鴨腳咁拎張紙巾捉左隻蟻再大大力揸左一下 <br />\n<br />\n但問題嚟啦 隻蟻揸唔死呀 啲手手腳腳瘋狂咁蠕動 嗰下真係頭皮麻晒 眼淚都標埋出嚟(我知我真係好撚廢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> )自問都幾大力咁揸多幾下都係無死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n咁唯有拎住隻蟻出廳搵老豆求救 老豆一手拎住隻蟻dum落馬桶再沖廁 點知隻蟻無沖走不特只 仲爬返出馬桶 最後係老豆搵馬桶刷硬生壓死佢 隻蟻先死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n宜家仲係好撚驚 驚到床都唔夠膽上 眼瞓都唔肯瞓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 諗住叫老豆幫手睇下張床仲有冇第二隻但係佢唔肯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n頭先真係太驚 唔記得左影低隻蟻個樣 同圖中呢一撚樣 我諗再大隻小小 話說我頭先淨係叫到啲圖 個背隻都寒埋頭皮又麻左 雞皮汗毛棟起晒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/23/024031_121c71d4e5c39fb987b342714b284c24.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F23%2F024031_121c71d4e5c39fb987b342714b284c24.jpg&h=29610c64&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n我知我驚蟻好奇怪 我反而唔驚曱甴老鼠嗰啲 連自己都唔知點解會驚埋啲咁細隻嘅昆蟲 但係又一直都克服唔到對蟻同蜂嘅恐懼 有冇巴絲同我一樣係好撚驚蟻or蜜蜂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e7cd13ac598e1cc2fec68c79762c24b4585bd0ed","tid":370043,"uid":135707,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-22T19:04:17.000Z","msg":"Btw我到宜家都仲係企左係到無上到床<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ed0ea829c05a8fd2ecd81ade81aca9aed4ede1a1","tid":370043,"uid":72638,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-22T19:06:45.000Z","msg":"至怕係起左巢<br />\n不過連登好多滅蟲聖手<br />\n又殺黃蜂又殺木蛩"},{"pid":"7277408cdaa513f7ce7bc5ba19331c87adbc2aaf","tid":370043,"uid":135707,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-22T19:08:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>至怕係起左巢<br />\n不過連登好多滅蟲聖手<br />\n又殺黃蜂又殺木蛩</blockquote><br />\n我都驚係起左巢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我老豆又話係野生俾風吹左入嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 但係我住20樓up 呢個理由總覺得牽強咗啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d6ae80823b33449c7cd877869a64aaa673fc9d99","tid":370043,"uid":72638,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-22T19:11:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>至怕係起左巢<br />\n不過連登好多滅蟲聖手<br />\n又殺黃蜂又殺木蛩</blockquote><br />\n我都驚係起左巢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我老豆又話係野生俾風吹左入嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 但係我住20樓up 呢個理由總覺得牽強咗啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n之前黃蜂post如果起左巢可以叫<br />\n食環處漁護處或滅蟲公司搞<br />\n你揾下多唔多 同揾下有冇巢先"},{"pid":"081d8a5b2290696d154041d63a15b77fd8d45a94","tid":370043,"uid":29745,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTi